high_descs: Turn right and walk to the kitchen shelves, then make a right and go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the pot in the center of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge and place the pot on the top shelf, then close the fridge. Wait a few seconds and then remove the pot.
Turn around, step forward, turn right, step forward, then turn right to face a cabinet door on the lower left.
Open the cabinet door and place the pot inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot in the fridge and place in the cabinet.

high_descs: Go to the right and then right again and stand in front of the sink.
Pick the pot up from the sink.
Go left and turn to face the fridge on the left.
Put the pot in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the pot up.
Move to the left and face the lower cabinet to the left of the fridge.
Put the pot in the cabinet to the left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot in the cabinet.

high_descs: pick up the pot from the sink
take the pot to the fridge
put the pot in the fridge then take back out
approach the bottom cabinet to the left of the fridge
put the pot in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: take the pot from the sink to the fridge followed by the putting it in the cabinet
